MotifGPT
========

A Motif-based LLM Chat Client.


Dependencies
------------

To build MotifGPT, you will need the following libraries and their development headers:

- A Motif implementation (e.g., OpenMotif, Lesstif)
- libcurl
- libcjson
- libdisasterparty


Building from Source
--------------------

    $ ./autogen.sh   # Only needed if building from a git clone
    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install